extendedInfo.description: The ChristianCafe.com Christian dating app allows you to meet fun Christian singles via your Android phone. New members can sign up directly via the app and enjoy a free trial of the service. Existing ChristianCafe.com members can simply log in just as they would at ChristianCafe.com. Meet fun Christian singles! Communicate free for 10 days (7 days free plus 3 more with a photo posted).Features:- create basic dating profile with free trial sign up- post a photo of yourself- perform detailed searches and favorite profiles that interest you- view detailed profiles, including photos- see who is online in your area- communicate via email and winksChristianCafe.com is the premier online dating service for Christian singles, connecting Christian singles since 1999. The service is Christian owned and has over 1,500 testimonials. Meet other Christian singles today by trying out the ChristianCafe.com Android dating app!

reviews.title: Worthless App
reviews.comment: First attempt to search 1) gave NO results if I used a single filter such as age range or ethnicity and then required inputting them again 2) would not save zipcode for location 3) would not use back arrow...it kept going to their landing screen 4) no way to filter by photo only profiles. 5) cannot see profile pics w/o setting up a profile 6) crashed my phone with the app open and using home button. HORRIBLY designed.
